755
00:54:06,327 --> 00:54:08,329
The man's a virus.

756
00:54:11,374 --> 00:54:12,667
Homicide, then.

757
00:54:13,167 --> 00:54:14,836
That's you, right?

758
00:54:17,338 --> 00:54:18,589
Yeah.

759
00:54:20,675 --> 00:54:24,011
I know it's hard right
now, detective, but...

760
00:54:24,095 --> 00:54:26,514
Try to think on this as a favor.

761
00:54:53,666 --> 00:54:55,001
This seems right.

762
00:54:56,043 --> 00:54:57,211
Yeah.

763
00:54:58,296 --> 00:55:00,965
So, I understand my old unit's gone
to lieutenant marimow.

764
00:55:01,048 --> 00:55:02,967
Yes, it has.

765
00:55:03,050 --> 00:55:04,552
So that unit is...

766
00:55:04,635 --> 00:55:07,096
- Yes, it is.
- That's a shame.

767
00:55:08,014 --> 00:55:10,850
I need to ask if you can
