and get the nurse.

792
00:56:43,484 --> 00:56:44,777
Everybody in your seats.

793
00:56:47,905 --> 00:56:49,907
Just lay still. Just lay still.

794
00:56:54,245 --> 00:56:56,914
Just keep putting pressure on it.

795
00:56:59,250 --> 00:57:02,003
You're doing fine.
Chiquan, you're doing fine.

796
00:57:02,086 --> 00:57:04,672
Just hold on for a couple more minutes.

797
00:57:06,966 --> 00:57:10,303
It's gonna be ok. It's gonna be ok.

798
00:57:21,188 --> 00:57:23,190
You're gonna be all right.

